com.appglu.android.sync
Class SyncListener

java.lang.Object
  com.appglu.android.sync.SyncListener

public abstract class SyncListener
extends Object

Create a sub-class of SyncListener to receive events from SyncIntentService.

To register and unregister the SyncListener use the SyncApi methods like below:

AppGlu.syncApi().registerSyncListener(syncListener);
AppGlu.syncApi().unregisterSyncListener(syncListener);

Since:
1.0.0
See Also:
SyncApi.registerSyncListener(SyncListener), SyncApi.unregisterSyncListener(SyncListener), SyncIntentService
